STATE EX REL. HAMILTON
v.
DEPT. OF HEALTH 2018-1236 Supreme Court of Ohio. January 23, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, Donnelly, and Stewart, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion for judicial notice denied.
